COVID19 Update(Nigeria): 
confirmed 0, deaths 0, recovered 0 Guys, the lockdown may have been eased across states in the country, but coronavirus cases continue to rise exponentially. We know the easing of the lockdown was done purely for economic reasons, not public health — Nigeria cannot afford to keep its citizens at home. So it’s important that while you go out there to make a living, please ensure you stay safe. Here’s how to do that: <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1408808" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Physical-Distancing.jpg?resize=680%2C680&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="680" data-recalc-dims="1" />
